    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine currently struggles to stay running, and there are significant leaks that need immediate attention. The exterior has several large dents and visible rust on the rocker panels, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It is not currently road-worthy and will likely need to be towed.",
      "price": 4500.0,
